    "description": "Manufactured OpenAPI artifact for commercetools HTTP API. This file was synthesized by Last Mile from curated research JSON and is not vendor-certified. Use it as an agent-consumable starting point, then validate paths, schemas, authentication, and server URLs with the vendor before production use. commercetools publicly describes its HTTP API as the canonical surface for resource representations, HTTP methods, project configuration, resource customization, and common behaviors such as reference expansion, optimistic concurrency control, and query features. The same public API hub also links a companion GraphQL API for network-efficient queries and mutations. This is a write-capable composable commerce platform for application and data-layer integration, but it does not represent asset or telemetry data. Asset data is Unsupported. Telemetry data is Unsupported. Writeback is Supported.",
